{% block output_section %}
## Output Requirements
{% if output_format %}
{{ output_format }}
{% endif %}

{% if verbosity == "comprehensive" %}
**Important:** Provide a comprehensive, thorough response leveraging your full analytical capabilities. Do not summarize or abbreviate. Use the available context depth.
